'''Claire Andrade-Watkins,''' ni umunyamateka akaba n'umukinnyi wa filimi ukomoka muri  [[Kapu Veri|Cape Verdean]] na [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika|Amerika]] . <ref>https://www.brown.edu/academics/college/swearer/people/practitioners-residence/claire-andrade-watkins-s2017-f2017</ref> Ni intiti itandukanye y’amateka nyafurika n yibanda ku mateka ya Amerika na Cape Verdean, ndetse n’Abafaransa nyuma y’abakoloni. Hagati aho, yitwaye neza muri sinema nyafurika ivuga [[Porutigali|Igiporutugali]], sinema za diaspora ya Africana, hamwe na firime y'Abanyamerika b'Abirabura ndetse n'abayikora. <ref name="MAPS">https://www.maps-inc.org/our-staff/claire-andrade-watkins-phd/</ref><ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=6627</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yize muri Lincoln School Providence, abona impamyabumenyi ya BA muri Simmons College nyuma abona MA na Ph.D. wo muri kaminuza ya Boston . <ref name="emerson">https://www.maps-inc.org/our-staff/claire-andrade-watkins-phd/</ref><ref>https://newenglandfilm.com/magazine/2016/06/cape-verdean-stories</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Andrade-Watkins ni Umuyobozi washinze umushinga wa ' Fox Point Cape Verdean ', umushinga w’ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu baturage mu 2007<ref>https://independent-magazine.org/2019/11/04/legacy-kind-funny-porto-rican-cape-verdean-american-story/</ref>. Afite isosiyete ikora kandi igakwirakwiza, 'SPIA Media Productions, Inc.' . Yashinzwe mu 1998 kandi izobereye mu bitangazamakuru byo muri [[Afurika]] Diaspora.  <ref>https://spiamedia.com/founder-president/</ref>

Niwe mwarimu wa mbere wigisha amasomo yamabara muri kaminuza, akaba na Porofeseri wambere wuzuye wamabara muri Visual and Media Arts mbere yo kwimukira mu kigo cyubuhanzi bwa Liberal Arts & Interdisciplinary Studies. Ni n'umwanditsi w'ibitabo byinshi birimo,''Society for Visual Anthropology'', ''Research in African Literature'', ''The Independent Film and Video Monthly'', ''American Historical Review'', and ''CinémActionn'' <ref>http://cinafrica.letras.ufrj.br/index.php/filmes/cabo-verde/170-claire-andrade-watkins</ref>.<ref>https://berkeleybeacon.com/emerson-professor-debuts-film/</ref>

